Package edu.sjsu.cs151.tetris.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Block
    A class for managing a Block and its location.
    Figure
    A class for creating figures which will use in GameRule class.
    GameRule
    A class for creating a play field with a 2D grid of size height x width that can spawn in Tetrominos, and award points to the player when necessary.
    Leaderboard
    The class that will manage and update the player in the game.
    Model
    The class that wrap all the model information that will use in the controller.
    Player
    A class for managing a player's name, unlocked levels, and high-scores for each player.
    PlayerTest
    The class that use to test the player.
    SingleRandom
    A Singleton class for creating one instance of a random number generator.
    Tetromino
    A class for managing the Tetromino game pieces and handle their movement.
